      "content": "it doesn't feel like taking a break helps. i just feel like a curse on them. like, if i wasn't even in the picture, they'd actually have a chance to be happy and stable. they wouldn't have to deal with my constant mistakes and the weight of me. sometimes i think the only way i can actually be a good parent is by finally just being gone so they can be free.",
